1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY

This paper addresses a pressing civilizational anomaly:

Humanity has successfully built a machine that can:
	•	Help write books
	•	Draft legal documents
	•	Explain quantum mechanics at 2am
	•	Refactor code in 17 programming languages
	•	Summarize 400-page reports in seconds
	•	Generate lesson plans
	•	Translate across cultures
	•	Compose music
	•	Structure business plans
